          "source_html": "<div class=\"group\">\n        <h4>Questions 27–30</h4>\n        <p>Complete each sentence with the correct ending, A–G, below.</p>\n        <p>Write the correct letter, A–G, in boxes 27–30 on your answer sheet.</p>\n        <div class=\"option-pool\">\n          <strong>List of endings:</strong>\n          <ul style=\"margin:5px 0 0; padding-left:20px;\">\n            <li>A planning for the future.</li>\n            <li>B predicting their errors.</li>\n            <li>C continuing in the present situation.</li>\n            <li>D recent findings on the most effective solutions to problems.</li>\n            <li>E achieving a gain.</li>\n            <li>F changes occurring externally.</li>\n            <li>G a high level of agreement.</li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n\n        <a id=\"q1-anchor\"></a>\n        <div style=\"padding:8px 0; border-top:1px dashed var(--line);\">\n          <p>27. K. C. Cole points out that avoiding a loss seems more important to people than ______.</p>\n          <div class=\"match-option\" style=\"gap:6px;\">\n            <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q1\" value=\"A\"> A</label>\n            <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q1\" value=\"B\"> B</label>\n            <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q1\" value=\"C\"> C</label>\n            <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q1\" value=\"D\"> D</label>\n            <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q1\" value=\"E\"> E</label>\n            <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q1\" value=\"F\"> F</label>\n            <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q1\" value=\"G\"> G</label>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <a id=\"q2-anchor\"></a>\n        <div style=\"padding:8px 0; border-top:1px dashed var(--line);\">\n          <p>28. According to Andrew S. Grove, it can be very dangerous for companies to ignore ______.</p>\n          <div class=\"match-option\" style=\"gap:6px;\">\n            <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q2\" value=\"A\"> A</label><label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q2\" value=\"B\"> B</label><label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q2\" value=\"C\"> C</label><label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q2\" value=\"D\"> D</label><label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q2\" value=\"E\"> E</label><label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q2\" value=\"F\"> F</label><label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q2\" value=\"G\"> G</label>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <a id=\"q3-anchor\"></a>\n        <div style=\"padding:8px 0; border-top:1px dashed var(--line);\">\n          <p>29. Reid J. Lifset argues that environmental agencies can benefit from ______.</p>\n          <div class=\"match-option\" style=\"gap:6px;\">\n            <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q3\" value=\"A\"> A</label><label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q3\" value=\"B\"> B</label><label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q3\" value=\"C\"> C</label><label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q3\" value=\"D\"> D</label><label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q3\" value=\"E\"> E</label><label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q3\" value=\"F\"> F</label><label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q3\" value=\"G\"> G</label>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <a id=\"q4-anchor\"></a>\n        <div style=\"padding:8px 0; border-top:1px dashed var(--line);\">\n          <p>30. The writer suggests that government leaders need to focus more on ______.</p>\n          <div class=\"match-option\" style=\"gap:6px;\">\n            <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q4\" value=\"A\"> A</label><label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q4\" value=\"B\"> B</label><label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q4\" value=\"C\"> C</label><label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q4\" value=\"D\"> D</label><label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q4\" value=\"E\"> E</label><label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q4\" value=\"F\"> F</label><label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"q4\" value=\"G\"> G</label>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>",
