          "source_html": "<div class=\"group\">\n        <h4>Questions 31–39</h4>\n        <p>The reading passage has eight paragraphs, <strong>A–H</strong>.</p>\n        <p>Which paragraph contains the following information?</p>\n        <p>Write the correct letter, <strong>A–H</strong>, in boxes 31–39 on your answer sheet.</p>\n        <p><em>NB You may use any letter more than once.</em></p>\n\n        <a id=\"q5-anchor\"></a><div style=\"padding:6px 0;\"><span class=\"question-number\">31.</span> the areas of study that help us understand risk\n          <div class=\"match-option\"><label>A<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q5\" value=\"A\"></label><label>B<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q5\" value=\"B\"></label><label>C<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q5\" value=\"C\"></label><label>D<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q5\" value=\"D\"></label><label>E<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q5\" value=\"E\"></label><label>F<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q5\" value=\"F\"></label><label>G<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q5\" value=\"G\"></label><label>H<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q5\" value=\"H\"></label></div>\n        </div>\n        <a id=\"q6-anchor\"></a><div style=\"padding:6px 0;\"><span class=\"question-number\">32.</span> reference to key actions that might benefit the world\n          <div class=\"match-option\"><label>A<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q6\" value=\"A\"></label><label>B<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q6\" value=\"B\"></label><label>C<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q6\" value=\"C\"></label><label>D<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q6\" value=\"D\"></label><label>E<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q6\" value=\"E\"></label><label>F<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q6\" value=\"F\"></label><label>G<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q6\" value=\"G\"></label><label>H<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q6\" value=\"H\"></label></div>\n        </div>\n        <a id=\"q7-anchor\"></a><div style=\"padding:6px 0;\"><span class=\"question-number\">33.</span> examples of statistical predictions that the majority of the public react to in the same way\n          <div class=\"match-option\"><label>A<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q7\" value=\"A\"></label><label>B<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q7\" value=\"B\"></label><label>C<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q7\" value=\"C\"></label><label>D<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q7\" value=\"D\"></label><label>E<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q7\" value=\"E\"></label><label>F<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q7\" value=\"F\"></label><label>G<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q7\" value=\"G\"></label><label>H<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q7\" value=\"H\"></label></div>\n        </div>\n        <a id=\"q8-anchor\"></a><div style=\"padding:6px 0;\"><span class=\"question-number\">34.</span> the variety of contexts in which risk occurs\n          <div class=\"match-option\"><label>A<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q8\" value=\"A\"></label><label>B<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q8\" value=\"B\"></label><label>C<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q8\" value=\"C\"></label><label>D<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q8\" value=\"D\"></label><label>E<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q8\" value=\"E\"></label><label>F<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q8\" value=\"F\"></label><label>G<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q8\" value=\"G\"></label><label>H<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q8\" value=\"H\"></label></div>\n        </div>\n        <a id=\"q9-anchor\"></a><div style=\"padding:6px 0;\"><span class=\"question-number\">35.</span> mention of a habit that has been proved to be very risky\n          <div class=\"match-option\"><label>A<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q9\" value=\"A\"></label><label>B<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q9\" value=\"B\"></label><label>C<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q9\" value=\"C\"></label><label>D<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q9\" value=\"D\"></label><label>E<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q9\" value=\"E\"></label><label>F<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q9\" value=\"F\"></label><label>G<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q9\" value=\"G\"></label><label>H<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q9\" value=\"H\"></label></div>\n        </div>\n        <a id=\"q10-anchor\"></a><div style=\"padding:6px 0;\"><span class=\"question-number\">36.</span> reference to market forces motivating change\n          <div class=\"match-option\"><label>A<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q10\" value=\"A\"></label><label>B<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q10\" value=\"B\"></label><label>C<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q10\" value=\"C\"></label><label>D<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q10\" value=\"D\"></label><label>E<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q10\" value=\"E\"></label><label>F<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q10\" value=\"F\"></label><label>G<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q10\" value=\"G\"></label><label>H<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q10\" value=\"H\"></label></div>\n        </div>\n        <a id=\"q11-anchor\"></a><div style=\"padding:6px 0;\"><span class=\"question-number\">37.</span> the writer's current attitude towards risk\n          <div class=\"match-option\"><label>A<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q11\" value=\"A\"></label><label>B<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q11\" value=\"B\"></label><label>C<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q11\" value=\"C\"></label><label>D<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q11\" value=\"D\"></label><label>E<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q11\" value=\"E\"></label><label>F<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q11\" value=\"F\"></label><label>G<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q11\" value=\"G\"></label><label>H<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q11\" value=\"H\"></label></div>\n        </div>\n        <a id=\"q12-anchor\"></a><div style=\"padding:6px 0;\"><span class=\"question-number\">38.</span> a reason why some individuals avoid making a career change\n          <div class=\"match-option\"><label>A<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q12\" value=\"A\"></label><label>B<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q12\" value=\"B\"></label><label>C<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q12\" value=\"C\"></label><label>D<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q12\" value=\"D\"></label><label>E<input type=\"radio\" name=\"q12\" value=\"E\"></label><label>F<input type=\"radio\"